org.biohipi.image.io.ImageDecoder

  • Packages that use ImageDecoder 
    Package Description
    org.biohipi.image.io
    A group of classes for reading (decoding) and writing (encoding) images in various storage formats such as JPEG, PNG, NIFTI, DICOM.

    • Uses of ImageDecoder in org.biohipi.image.io

      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  DicomCodec
      Class for objects that serve as both an ImageDecoder and ImageEncoder for the DICOM image storage format.

      Extends RasterCodec and serves as both an ImageDecoder and ImageEncoder for the JPEG image storage format.
      class  NiftiCodec
      Class for objects that serve as both an ImageDecoder and ImageEncoder for the Nifti image storage format.
      class  PngCodec
      Extends RasterCodec and serves as both an ImageDecoder and ImageEncoder for the PNG image storage format.
      class  RasterCodec
      Abstract base class for objects that serve as both an ImageDecoder and ImageEncoder for a particular storage format (e.g., JPEG, PNG).

      Find a ImageDecoder capable of deserializing a BioHipiImage object stored in a specific BioHipiImageHeader.BioHipiImageFormat.
